  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators hypothesize that schoolchildren treated with IPT using DP over one year of
      follow-up will have a different risk of clinical malaria compared to those treated with
      placebo.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
